title: Mayor’s new Tech Map reveals businesses are booming in London (Greater London Authority)
text: ( Source : Greater London Authority ) London's science and technology industry is booming and 90, 000 businesses in the capital now employ approximately 700,000 people, according to a new interactive map unveiled by the Mayor of London , Boris
